## Frontend auth (current)

- **Screens:** Company SignUp, Veterinary SignUp, Login, Forgot password, Reset password; multi-step forms for signups.
- **UI:** Native components (HTML + Tailwind); shared components in `frontend/src/components/` (e.g. Button, FieldWithError, StepIndicator, StepLayout). Auth footer links and signup step forms live under `frontend/src/app/(auth)/components/` and `(auth)/signup/company/`, `(auth)/signup/veterinary/` (CompanyStep1–3Form, VeterinaryStep1–3Form).
- **Login:** Single credential form (no role); backend provides "get user type by email"; app redirects to `/dashboard/company` or `/dashboard/veterinary` based on user type.
- **API:** Auth flows use mocks (auth API layer in `frontend/src/auth/api/`). Swagger documented and Orval regenerated; ready to swap mocks for generated hooks when integrating with backend.
- **Placeholder routes:** `/dashboard/company`, `/dashboard/veterinary` for post-login redirect.
